st updates on this service.</em>","Frontpoint is a self-install home security system with DIY home automation add-ons. The system monitors your home against intruders and burglars. Since the company’s focus lies in home security, there isn’t much of an emphasis on DIY home automation products to help bring convenience to your home. Frontpoint offers customer support and helpful installation guides.","Sensors and security cameras are the main strengths in Frontpoint’s system. However, Frontpoint also sells light controls, smart locks and thermostats to help round out your DIY home automation system. Each of these add-ons brings a little more convenience and remote access to your home. You control the system using the Frontpoint mobile app, which is available for Android and iOS smartphones.","In terms of home control technology, Frontpoint supports DIY home automation products that use Z-Wave. The system’s control panel can access Wi-Fi, which allows it to communicate with the mobile app and security but no other smart home products. The Frontpoint DIY home automation system doesn’t support Bluetooth and ZigBee devices, which is common among DIY home automation systems that emphasize security.","Frontpoint offers three home security monitoring plans that you can get on a one- or three-year contract. Of the three plans, the cheapest doesn’t support DIY home automation control. The middle plan only adds lighting control to your system, while the most expensive plan gives you access to all of Frontpoint’s DIY home automation features. Each of the three plans includes 24-hour home security monitoring that helps protect your home. When you call the company, a sales representative walks you through the process to help you find the right plan and devices to fit your home automation needs.","To speed up and simplify the installation process, Frontpoint programs your system before shipping. When you get the DIY home automation system, you follow the included tutorials to install it in your home. Frontpoint’s customer support options include video tutorials and device manuals. You can contact Frontpoint support via email and telephone – the company does not have live chat support. All Frontpoint systems have a three-year warranty that replaces malfunctioning smart home devices."]},"id":"def188c0-e076-4386-a2d2-b92d935decd5","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_68182","url":"/frontpoint-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"john-carlsen","url":"/author/john-carlsen","dateCreated":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","name":"John Carlsen","dateModified":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","id":"jN6fuw55cS2xYQi25mfgkg","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2016-08-05T18:00:13Z","datePublished":"2016-08-05T18:00:13Z","name":"Frontpoint Secure Package","synopsis":"Editor's Note: Frontpoint has been removed from our DIY home automation systems comparison and this page is no longer being updated, please visit our home security systems review for the latest updates on this service.","review":{"pros":[""],"cons":[""]},"strapline":"Editor's Note: Frontpoint has been removed from our DIY home automation systems comparison and this page is no longer being updated, please visit our home security systems review for the latest updates on this service.","language":"en","dateModified":"2016-08-05T18:00:13Z","id":"KwGnFLMSLPeGzAddkVksaA","meta":{"title":"Frontpoint Review | Top Ten Reviews","description":"Frontpoint has a few DIY home automation options that you can add to your home security system. Read here to learn more."},"products":[{"slug":"frontpoint-secure-package","url":"/product/frontpoint-secure-package","dateCreated":"2019-04-16T19:43:23Z","name":"Frontpoint Secure Package","dateModified":"2019-04-16T19:43:23Z","id":"gw7CBdTUjktu2DEgRtMRFP","dateImported":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","site":"toptenreviews"}],"dateImported":"2019-04-16T19:43:23Z","type":"review","template":"review","social"